Lingua/FA/Number version 0.01
========================

Lingua::FA::Number

   English to Farsi (Persian) Number Convertor

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 None!

